nvidia-graphics-drivers-450 (450.66-0ubuntu2) groovy; urgency=medium

  * debian/templates/control.in:
    - Add the XB-PmAliases field, so that ubuntu-drivers can
      check RTD3 support from the apt cache, and enable it
      on installation.
    - Add build-dependency on python3 (for pm-aliases-gen).
  * debian/pm-aliases-gen,
    debian/rules:
    - Include and use the pm-aliases-gen tool to extract the IDs
      from the json database.

